Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.34,0:22:03.01,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HFFF7FB&\shad2\pos(320,462)}我仍然在你背后向你招手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.01,0:22:14.65,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HFFF7FB&\shad2\pos(330,462)}在昨天之前 似乎什么事都没发生般
