Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.99,0:22:23.91,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HFFF7FB&\shad2\pos(320,462)}一点小事也要争吵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.91,0:22:29.92,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HFFF7FB&\shad2\pos(320,462)}会不会有一天我们再也不能见面
