Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.47,0:23:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小去那里了?噢?点心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.66,0:23:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小 小小
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.07,0:23:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?要给我吗?谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.81,0:23:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你从哪里拿到的呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.42,0:23:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小 小小
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.80,0:23:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是糖果王国吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.91,0:23:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小 小小
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.34,0:23:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像浪费时间一样…笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.65,0:23:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水手之星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.76,0:23:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小之谜?超级追击行动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.82,0:23:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月光传递着爱的讯息


